<h2>%%ReferenceStyle%%Book, six or more authors</h2>
<hr>
<br>
<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Authors. (Year of publication). <em>Title of book</em>. Place of publication: Publisher.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Examples</strong>
<br>
When authors number up to and including seven, include all the authors&#8217; names.
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Authors">Smith, A., Brown, B., Chan, C., Williams, D., Tahatai, M., &amp; Singh, R.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">The decline and fall of the modern generation</span></em>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Parramatta, Australia</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">New Media Press</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
When authors number eight or more, include the first six authors&#8217; names, then insert three 
ellipses (full stops/periods), and add the last author&#8217;s name.
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Authors">Smith, A., Brown, B., Chan, C., Williams, D., Tahatai, M., Jones, A., &hellip; Singh, R.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">The decline and fall of the modern generation</span></em>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Parramatta, Australia</span>:  
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">New Media Press</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
For a numbered edition, place the abbreviation in parenthesis after the book title. This part should 
not be italicised. Use (Rev. ed.) for revised editions.
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Authors">Smith, A., Brown, B., Chan, C., Williams, D., Tahatai, M., Jones, A., &hellip; Singh, R.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">The decline and fall of the modern generation</span></em> 
	(<span class="hover" title="edition">2nd ed.</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Parramatta, Australia</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">New Media Press</span>.
</blockquote>
